  },
  {
    id: '4',
    sender: 'ai' as const,
    message: '<strong>üö® ADDITIONAL CRITICAL DISCREPANCIES:</strong>\n\n**2. Payment Terms - CASH FLOW IMPACT**\n‚Ä¢ CloudTech: **Net 15 days** (aggressive)\n‚Ä¢ DataFlow: **Net 45 days** (standard)\n‚Ä¢ SecureOps: **Net 60 days** (favorable to us)\n\n**3. Termination Rights - MAJOR IMBALANCE**\n‚Ä¢ CloudTech: **90-day notice required** + penalty fees\n‚Ä¢ DataFlow: **30-day notice** (mutual)\n‚Ä¢ SecureOps: **Immediate termination** for cause allowed\n\n**4. Data Ownership - CONFLICTING TERMS**\n‚Ä¢ CloudTech: Vendor retains **rights to derived insights** üò±\n‚Ä¢ DataFlow: **Customer owns all data** ‚úÖ\n‚Ä¢ SecureOps: **Unclear ownership** of security logs\n\n**5. Auto-Renewal Mechanisms**\n‚Ä¢ CloudTech: **Auto-renews for 2 years** unless 120-day notice\n‚Ä¢ DataFlow: **Annual auto-renewal** with 60-day notice\n‚Ä¢ SecureOps: **Month-to-month** after initial term',
    timestamp: '11:21 AM'
  },
  {
    id: '5',
    sender: 'user' as const,
    message: 'This is eye-opening! Can you create a risk matrix and suggest which contracts need immediate attention?',
    timestamp: '11:22 AM'
  },
  {
    id: '6',
    sender: 'ai' as const,
    message: '<strong>üéØ RISK PRIORITIZATION MATRIX</strong>\n\n**üî¥ IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED:**\n\n**CloudTech Contract - HIGH RISK**\n‚Ä¢ **Risk Score: 9.2/10** ‚ö†Ô∏è\n‚Ä¢ **Issues:** Unlimited liability + aggressive terms\n‚Ä¢ **Financial Exposure:** Potentially unlimited\n‚Ä¢ **Action:** Negotiate liability cap IMMEDIATELY\n\n**üü° MEDIUM PRIORITY:**\n\n**SecureOps Contract - MEDIUM RISK** \n‚Ä¢ **Risk Score: 6.1/10**\n‚Ä¢ **Issues:** Unclear data ownership + excessive liability cap\n‚Ä¢ **Action:** Clarify data rights within 30 days\n\n**üü¢ LOW RISK:**\n\n**DataFlow Contract - LOW RISK**\n‚Ä¢ **Risk Score: 2.8/10** ‚úÖ\n‚Ä¢ **Issues:** Minor - mostly favorable terms\n‚Ä¢ **Action:** Use as template for future contracts\n\n<strong>üí° STRATEGIC RECOMMENDATIONS:</strong>\n1. **Standardize liability caps** across all vendors (suggest $1M max)\n2. **Harmonize payment terms** to Net 30-45 days\n3. **Implement consistent data ownership** clauses\n4. **Create master vendor agreement template** based on DataFlow terms',
    timestamp: '11:24 AM',
    documents: [
      {
        name: 'Vendor_Contract_Risk_Analysis.xlsx',
        type: 'xlsx' as const,
        size: '1.4 MB'
      },
      {
        name: 'Contract_Discrepancy_Report.pdf',
        type: 'pdf' as const,
        size: '2.1 MB'
