            Reveals where your organization lacks consistent negotiation standards, 
            leading to different terms for similar services.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-yellow-200">
            <p class="text-xs text-yellow-700 font-medium">Example: Payment terms ranging from Net 15 to Net 60 days</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Strategic Opportunities -->
        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Strategic Opportunities</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
            Identifies your strongest contracts as templates for future negotiations 
            and highlights vendor relationships to prioritize.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 border border-green-200">
            <p class="text-xs text-green-700 font-medium">Example: DataFlow contract terms as gold standard template</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Insight -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Power of Perspective</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        <span class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold">Humans see documents one at a time. AI sees the forest AND the trees.</span>
        Cross-document analysis reveals systemic issues, hidden patterns, and strategic opportunities 
        that only become visible when you can hold multiple complex documents in perfect memory simultaneously.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">98%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Discrepancies Found vs Manual Review</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">15min</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Analysis Time vs 8+ Hours Manual</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">$2M</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Average Risk Exposure Identified</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>